description:
BEFORE THE MANSION.BEFORE THE DISASTER.

EVIL IS BORN.

Sent to investigate a series of grisly murders in Raccoon
City, S.T.A.R.S. Bravo Team scrambles into action. On the
way to the scene, Bravo's helicopter crashes. Although
everyone survives, what they discover next is gruesome:
an overturned military transport truck riddled with corpses
and that's only the beginning of their nightmare. Bravo
Team is about to discover the evil that is growing all around
them, and rookie member Rebecca Chambers is beginning to
wonder what she's gotten herself into.


Resident Evil Book 0 Zero Hour
By: S. D. Perry
Language: EN
Format: PDF
Pages: 216
